# TaskFlow Pro - Environment Variables
# This is a static app with no backend, so no environment variables are required.
# If you later add a backend, you can add Supabase credentials here.

# Example for future Supabase integration:
# SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key